Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.62,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※這裡練習的是「Lip slurs」技法\N\h\h\h\h透過嘴唇和氣流的變化來改變音高，維持聲音的平穩是一個難點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲音有點不太穩定 請各自注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仔細聽 確認自己和周圍人的聲音 不要走音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼休息五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上廁所的同學盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期中考也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們終於開始認真以比賽為目標的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了之後要舉行的試音做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們各自都專心練習要在比賽上演奏的樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵學姐要去上補習班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 抱歉 那接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:51.67,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\blur2\bord1.8\3c&HAA6D5B&\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(740,520)}愛哭鬼薩克斯風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田邊同學 開場樂段雖然是強後即弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:05.58,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fscy90\fad(300,300)}※強弱法中，力度記號p（piano）指弱，f（forte）指強，而fp（fortepiano）指強後立即變弱。\N\h\h\h\h像fp這樣的記號被稱作accent記號，所謂accent，是指藉由強弱變化凸顯某個音。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但請將重音演奏得更強烈一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回答得很不錯 不過褲子的拉鍊沒拉好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼從頭再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝指點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐 今天可以一起回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是獨奏部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明都有香織學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有規定一年級不可以做獨奏練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前就跟你說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒有無視人家或是做些討人厭的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練習結束了 收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 不是挺聽話的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 香織學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 你們還是先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就整理完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 好像要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠我也很喜歡下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能幫忙將那張椅子放回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放進倉庫裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要帶樂器回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶爾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們擋路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繞過去就好了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小女子抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們一直都這樣水火不容的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵這麼說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我跟她說至少到比賽前再加把勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之暫時是挽留下來了 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵她有自己的固執啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向明日香說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 但她說人家有升學考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}硬要想退出的人留下來也不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很有明日香的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小葵要退出？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 秀一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說到這一帶不花錢也能躲雨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概就是這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你剛才聽到了吧 葵學姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是故意不告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是昨天才從長號的學長那聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼偏偏是現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明比賽結束 三年級的社團活動也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然也只是學長的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過會不會和去年的事有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「去年」是指現在的二年級有很多成員退出的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過那是小葵高一年級和低一年級之間產生的問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是沒有直接關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過畢竟身處其中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以可能也發生了不少事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以沒有學長姐肯談去年的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷彿跨過夏天 直接步入秋季一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我感受到了有些淒涼的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但就算如此 我卻不知道哪來的樂觀 認為小葵應該不會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二天 那個瞬間突然就到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛剛那個地方 薩克斯風再吹一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吹到雙簧管獨奏為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}節奏不連貫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請更平滑地將聲音串起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平穩地帶起雙簧管的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}次中音薩克斯風 開頭音色不夠平穩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個一個來 齋藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了 齋藤葵同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛剛那一處什麼時候才能吹好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很遺憾 比賽不會等人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要定好一個期限 在那之前完成課題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不這樣提高水平 就無法有出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一段需要用美妙的和聲來支撐主旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在次中音薩克斯風的部分只剩你音色渾濁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你忙於準備考試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你同時也是面臨比賽的管樂社社員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再問一次 什麼時候才能吹好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要退出管樂社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果繼續這樣參與社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許就上不了想報考的大學了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經煩惱很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}考慮到以後花在練習上的時間會更長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒辦法再繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等請來辦公室一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}齋藤學姐 請不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的要離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前說過了吧 我高中沒考好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我一定要考上想去的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練習太辛苦的話 可以不用參加比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一開始就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的管樂社和去年不一樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日昇祭時我就感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不止是瀧老師 大家都是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都為了在比賽裡拿到金獎而努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒辦法做到那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能輕輕鬆鬆地朝著全國大賽努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明去年都沒能阻止她們離開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正我也真的必須準備考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣心裡也能更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試音加油啊 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然…我當不了社長的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是明日香是社長的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不會變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用說了 我一開始就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼不是明日香而是由我擔任社長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒這麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小笠原學姐也有很多優點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你說來聽聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會照顧人 又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對學弟妹也會打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時候還會帶小點心 很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不就只是溫柔而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「你很溫柔」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是對沒有其他優點的人的說詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹嘛沒完沒了纏著學妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當自己是蛇啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒纏著她 你來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出來這麼久了還不回去 大家都很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前你先回音樂教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 把眼淚擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己會擦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這情緒不穩的毛病得改改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前香織不是也跟你說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當社長就要堂堂正正 別杞人憂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你來當社長不就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你拒絕了 我才不得不當的 明…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你也拒絕掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:17.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(230,65)}小號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:17.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBDA40F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(223,60)}小號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\1c&H000000&\pos(876,142)\org(881.333,143.333)\frz333.3\frx38\fry334}退社申請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\1c&H000000&\pos(746,152)\frx8\fry354\frz332}姓名 齋藤葵 班級 3年6班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\1c&H000000&\pos(608,220)\frx358\fry352\frz329.6}因為如下理由，希望退出{\u1}管樂社{\u0}，提交本表。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\1c&H000000&\pos(658,292)\frx32\fry352\frz330.3}退社理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\1c&H000000&\pos(580,322)\frx4\fry352\frz328.6}希望集中精神準備考試。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上低音號 剛剛你們吹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼不吹 不需要調音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好好吹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}204小節開始 低音聲部單獨再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前同學 是不是有點慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能吹好的音一直沒吹好 請集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝指點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是第一次看到你被批得那麼狠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天諸事不宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說音樂一旦被演奏出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就無法再收回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}演奏時要銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太在意也沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是葵學姐的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她要準備升學考 這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你果然很在意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏紀學姐 請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去年啊 是有不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐為什麼會留在社裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是我沒什麼幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過那時候我覺得那樣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想 管樂不像足球是靠分數決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}管樂比賽上判定的終究也是評委
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被這種不可靠的評價左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許有違音樂本身的樂趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒幹勁的學長姐們是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我那時候也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過這其實只是不想辛苦練習的藉口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為同年級的要我們認真練的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們徹底無視他們了 就像根本不存在一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到他們消失為止一直無視著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好過分 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是沒人對此有所意見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟對方是高年級的 又很嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是香織學姐和葵學姐還是努力維持著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們沒有跟著無視低年級
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還會聽取雙方的意見 在兩邊斡旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是他們還是走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴香學姐 葵學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有香織學姐現在大概會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「如果那時候能阻止他們退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在會是什麼樣子」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概只有明日香學姐不會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她去年沒站在哪一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和現在完全一樣 一直保持中立
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過換句話說 今年的氣氛就是與去年截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就連那麼沒幹勁的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都稍微提起了點興致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無視嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 香織學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 又先走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好…香織？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去路上不吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚餐裝在另一個胃裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想吃的話就來點薯條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 不是去年入社真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣的話我可能也會退出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠我可能會堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我喜歡音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會認同你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼在這個季節吃烤地瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想配著牛奶吃 很搭吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好歹也是管樂社的瑪丹娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是瑪丹娜也喜歡烤地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練習是明日香負責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟是副社長 就一帆風順地完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 我看到她的表現後就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香不是拒絕當社長 而是當不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概 在那時接管這個社需要很大的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香很聰明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是考慮到了這一切 才覺得做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我不就像個笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「這樣啊」？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我是說你真的很有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且至少高年級生都知道這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正因為那時晴香願意當社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}管樂社才能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是因為瀧老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 我倒認為是晴香的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊 明明是明日香派
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為她很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我作為演奏者 也能捨棄一切全情投入…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三心二意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我隱約也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說來說去 我還是很在意明日香的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}禁不住薯條的誘惑吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中薯條單一價錢的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.17,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃檗 黃檗站到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.10,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}月台在左側車門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.64,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下車的乘客請注意腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然可能幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是想談心的話 儘管來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會聽你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別客氣 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社長果然好像因為昨天的事請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然明日香學姐沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萬一社長不做了 田中學姐會接任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她才沒不做呢 別說奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}假設而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得田中學姐很難相處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐嗎 挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該說是太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或者說不知道她什麼時候是演戲什麼時候是真情流露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟久美子說這種話 你可能會生我氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我想我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺明日香學姐所注視的和我們完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天請假了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體恢復了 今天我會好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是什麼值得鼓掌的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託接下來可要拿全勤獎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就是為了調戲樂器才留在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼調音至降B調
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在也不能回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放棄後我才明白 這是必然的結果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我果然沒有那麼喜歡管樂社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停 那麼下一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有葵的管樂社有了新的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 全蛋餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子 你在和長號的塚本交往嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奏響了新的一曲
